================
pytest-slow-last
================

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/pytest-slow-last.svg
    :target: https://pypi.org/project/pytest-slow-last
    :alt: PyPI version

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/pytest-slow-last.svg
